OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny showers
OL,6,Fmostly easing this evening to leave
OL,7,Fclearer spells overnight. A few
OL,8,Fshowers still possible during the
OL,9,Fearly hours but most places dry. Mild
OL,10,Fand turning windier later.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FA cloudy and windy day with
OL,13,Fshowery rain, this heavy at times,
OL,14,Fespecially through the afternoon.
OL,15,FStrong southwesterly winds developing,
OL,16,Fwith gales likely in coastal and
OL,17,Fupland regions. Mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
