OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FColder
OL,6,Fon Friday with bright intervals and
OL,7,Fshowers, these frequent in places and
OL,8,Fpossibly wintry over the moors.
OL,9,FShowery on Saturday then perhaps more
OL,10,Fgenerally wetter on Sunday.
OL,11,FOccasionally breezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
